e. For example, if you want to know how much battery life the device has, simply text&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" class=""><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0);" class="">@30</span></strong>to the device and you'll receive a text message back indicating the current battery level.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(105, 105, 105);" class="">Alerts are a valuable way to interact with the device remotely, there a variety of special shortcodes to use check out Version 2.7 to explore them all.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(105, 105, 105);" class="">In this release we've also added the Message Results API which allows SMSsync to send the status of sent messages to the server.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(105, 105, 105);" class="">For more details,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.ushahidi.com/2014/10/27/smssync-v2-7/" class="">check out our blog post on this release</a>. If you have any questions or comments, don't hesitate to send us a note!</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(105, 105, 105);" class=""><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" class=""><font size="3" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" class="">Offering Support and Customization!</font></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(105, 105, 105);" class="">Are you interested in receiving any technical support, hosting, or customization for your SMSsync integration?&nbsp;<a href="mailto:henry@...?subject=SMSsync%3A%20Interested%20in%20Support!" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 166, 203);" class="">Send us an email</a>&nbsp;if you are interested, we are here to help!</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; c